It is a private higher education institution located in the large town of Ile Ife with a (population range of 50,000-249,999 inhabitants), Osun. 
The university is Officially accredited and recognized by the National Universities Commission of Nigeria as a higher education institution. The university is ranked 104 in the country and has a world rank of 10617. 
Oduduwa University offers courses and programs leading to officially recognized higher education degrees in several areas of study. 
