The Gospel Faith Mission International (GOFAMINT) is a major Christian denomination from Nigeria founded by Reuben Akinwalere George in Iwaya Yaba in 1956.[1] 
The Gospel Faith Mission International is present in numerous countries, such as Britain since 1983[2] and the United States since 1985.[3] 
