Adeola is a graduate of Art history.[5] She had previously worked at the Marketing and Communications at Stanbic IBTC and she was also an associate Producer at RED TV before going into documentary film making.[6][7] She was an assistant producer on the creation of the novel Half of a Yellow Sun which was adapted into a movie. 
