She has won 1 singles titles on the ITF Women's Circuit. 
Her only WTA Tour main draw appearance came at the 2008 Grand Prix SAR La Princesse Lalla Meryem.[1] 
Playing for Morocco at the Fed Cup, Essaadi has a win–loss record of 3–0.[2] 
