Lagos Baptist Academy is a secondary school located in Obanikoro, Lagos, Nigeria. 
The school was established in 1855 by the American Baptist Missionaries.[1][2] The school is regarded as a sister school to Reagan Memorial Baptist Girls' Secondary School, Yaba, Lagos and Baptist Girls' Academy, Obanikoro, Lagos. 
