Nancy Illoh is a Nigerian journalist. 
She is the presenter of the MoneyShow[1] on African Independent Television and also the media consultant and Channel Manager of Africa Business Channel in Daarsat.[2] She is the Chief Executive Officer of African Economic Congress.[3] 
